From 22b7ff3115a383c15ae6a29dc72b75db9c50f1a0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: fi3 <email@email.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 12:03:54 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 2/3] ADD interruptible selected-agent slash commands so
 backend commands bypass normal chat sends

Selected chat input beginning with a slash is executed through the backend command path instead of the ordinary send path. Codex resumes the selected thread with raw command stdin and registers that process under the selected agent so interrupts can stop it.
